node.text:
Turning looks, stunting pretty... it’s the queen from New York City coming at you for the final week of the #razr #FlipYourLook fashion challenge!! For this week, we are clearing the cobwebs and opening up our eyes to the dusty and hidden fashion gems in our closet! A drag queen telling you to head to the closet is almost unheard of, but I can’t wait wait to see all the fierce looks you turn out! #MotoPartner 
Here’s all the tea and details:
1. Post your fiercest Spring Cleaning inspired look. Re-style, re-purpose, and re-imagine your favorite garments and accessories in a fierce new way!
2. Tag #flipyourlook @motorolaus and @ageofaquaria
3. For every look posted, @motorolaus will donate $50 to the Ali Forney Center for Covid-19 relief funds, especially supporting homeless LGBTQ+ youth

Official Rules @ bit.ly/flipyourlook
